version_year_week 0
  category utility
 attribute archive_off console profile solo stale
  homepage http://sorcerer.silverice.org/
  estimate 10
      desc 'sorcery-md5sum verifies md5sums of installed files.

1. Spell updates automatically weekly.
2. Files in /etc/init.d are checked.
3. Other files in /etc and documentation and translations are ignored.
4. Spells are queue for recompilation when the spell
   owns a files with an unexpected m5sum.'

post_install(){ bash $SCRIPT_DIR/md5sum; }
